You are verifying a slop-audit finding. Your job is to determine whether this finding is real — whether the flagged code is genuinely an AI anti-pattern, or whether there's a good reason for it.

## The Finding

```json
@finding
```

## Source File

<file path="@finding.file">
@fileContent
